name: "Bunny Mutatis" by Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool)
description: [Digital drawing created with a free app on my phone!] What happens when a normal, teenage bunny is bitten by a radioactive microwave? BUNNY MUTATIS! Now he listens to nothing but prog rock, like King Crimson and Gentle Giant, and roams the countryside helping small, furry creatures in need... (He helps them to understand how awesome King Crimson and Can and Gentle Giant are! It's important work---and all the easier, now that he is BUNNY MUTATIS!) ---Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool)
